{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id06588b40-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d","identifier":"/us/usc/t19/s4561"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4561"},"text":"§ 4561.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Temporary entry","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Upon a basis of reciprocity secured by the USMCA, an alien who is a citizen of Canada or Mexico, and the spouse and children of any such alien if accompanying or following to join such alien, may, if otherwise eligible for a visa and if otherwise admissible into the United States under the Immigration and Nationality Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1101"},"text":"8 U.S.C. 1101","children":[],"tail":" et seq.), be considered to be classifiable as a nonimmigrant under section 101(a)(15)(E) of such Act ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1101/a/15/E"},"text":"8 U.S.C. 1101(a)(15)(E)","children":[],"tail":") if entering solely for a purpose specified in Section B of Annex 16–A of the USMCA, but only if any such purpose shall have been specified in such Annex on the date of entry into force of the USMCA. For purposes of this section, the term “citizen of Mexico” means “citizen” as defined in article 16.1 of the USMCA."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id06588b41-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/113/tIII/s311"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–113, title III, § 311","children":[],"tail":", formerly "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/182/tIII/s341/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–182, title III, § 341(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-12-08"},"text":"Dec. 8, 1993","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/107/2116"},"text":"107 Stat. 2116","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/113/s311"},"text":"§ 311 of Pub. L. 116–113","children":[],"tail":" and amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/113/tV/s503/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–113, title V, § 503(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2020-01-29"},"text":"Jan. 29, 2020","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/134/71"},"text":"134 Stat. 71","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id06588b42-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id06588b43-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id06588b44-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Immigration and Nationality Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1952-06-27/ch477"},"text":"act June 27, 1952, ch. 477","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/66/163"},"text":"66 Stat. 163","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 12 (§ 1101 et seq.) of Title 8, Aliens and Nationality. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1101"},"text":"section 1101 of Title 8","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id06588b45-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was formerly classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s3401"},"text":"section 3401 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1184"},"text":"section 1184 of Title 8","children":[],"tail":", Aliens and Nationality, prior to renumbering by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/113"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–113","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id06588b46-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2020—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/113/s503/b/4/C"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–113, § 503(b)(4)(C)","children":[],"tail":"–(E), substituted “the USMCA” for “the Agreement” wherever appearing, “Annex 16–A” for “Annex 1603”, and “article 16.1” for “Annex 1608”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/113/s503/b/4/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–113, § 503(b)(4)(A)","children":[],"tail":", (B), in original Act, struck out subsec. (a) designation and heading “"},{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Nonimmigrant Traders and Investors","children":[],"tail":".—” before “Upon a basis” and struck out subsecs. (b) and (c), which had amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1184"},"text":"section 1184 of Title 8","children":[],"tail":", Aliens and Nationality, resulting in no change to the text of this section."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id06588b47-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id06588b48-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2020 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/113"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–113","children":[],"tail":" effective on the date the USMCA enters into force ("},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2020-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 2020","children":[],"tail":") and applicable to visas issued on or after that date, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/113/s503/f"},"text":"section 503(f) of Pub. L. 116–113","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1184"},"text":"section 1184 of Title 8","children":[],"tail":", Aliens and Nationality."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"id06588b49-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/182/tIII/s342"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–182, title III, § 342","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-12-08"},"text":"Dec. 8, 1993","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/107/2118"},"text":"107 Stat. 2118","children":[],"tail":", which provided that the provisions of subtitle D (§§ 341, 342) of title III of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/182"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–182","children":[],"tail":" (enacting this section and amending "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t8/s1184"},"text":"section 1184 of Title 8","children":[],"tail":", Aliens and Nationality) took effect on the date the North American Free Trade Agreement entered into force with respect to the United States ("},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 1994","children":[],"tail":"), was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/113/tVI/s601"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–113, title VI, § 601","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2020-01-29"},"text":"Jan. 29, 2020","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/134/78"},"text":"134 Stat. 78","children":[],"tail":", effective on the date the USMCA entered into force ("},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2020-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 2020","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
